  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"ZBrushVectorDisplacement-ExportOBJandOpenEXRfromZBrush\">Export OBJ and OpenEXR from ZBrush</h3><ul><li><p> Shift+d to step down to the <strong>lowest subdivision. </strong>Lion Sculpted by Olivier Drion.</p></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"zbrush_highestSubdiv.png\" width=\"390\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_highestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=390&amp;height=365\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/zbrush_highestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"534\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540820\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"zbrush_highestSubdiv.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"afbf6fbb-490e-4374-896b-8aa01d96ef05\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_highestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=780&amp;height=730 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_highestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=390&amp;height=365 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png\" width=\"409\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=364\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"485\" data-width=\"544\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"034a3630-5782-44a7-b835-22915b6bcd54\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=818&amp;height=728 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_lowestSubdiv.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=364 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><ul><li><p> Hit the Switch button in<strong> Morph Target </strong> <strong>to switch to the original model</strong>.  If you don't have a Morph Target setup, please consult ZBrush documentation on how to set up a Morph Target.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_morphTarget.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=334&amp;height=348\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/zbrush_morphTarget.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"472\" data-width=\"452\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540835\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"zbrush_morphTarget.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"111a46aa-02f6-4322-a824-4f44637f949d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_morphTarget.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=452&amp;height=472 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_morphTarget.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=334&amp;height=348 1x\"></span><p>Hit the Switch button in<strong> Morph Target </strong> <strong>to switch to the original model</strong>.  If you don't have a Morph Target setup, please consult ZBrush documentation on how to set up a Morph Target.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_originalModel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=541\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/zbrush_originalModel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1006\" data-width=\"1114\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540850\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"zbrush_originalModel.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"48352cb1-890a-4a1c-b9fd-5ee3a208b1d8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_originalModel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1114&amp;height=1006 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_originalModel.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=541 1x\"></span><ul><li><p>In Preferences, Import/Export, Vector Displacement Map, set the <strong>Tangent FlipAndSwitch to 43.</strong>  There are 48 different vector displacement because a red channel for a renderer may be up while down for the another renderer.  RenderMan is 43.</p></li></ul><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"08939b01-988d-409c-9968-912d24fc16bd\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Recent changes meant a change from Tangent FlipAndSwitch 41, if your displacement is not correct, you may need this setting rather than 43.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"362\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/Zbrush-VD-Tangent-Flip-Switch.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563576&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=220&amp;height=324\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/Zbrush-VD-Tangent-Flip-Switch.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563576&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"324\" data-width=\"220\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540862\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Zbrush-VD-Tangent-Flip-Switch.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"5c5cbf3c-8cbb-4f7a-8ec7-06c182531262\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/Zbrush-VD-Tangent-Flip-Switch.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563576&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=220&amp;height=324 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/Zbrush-VD-Tangent-Flip-Switch.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563576&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=220&amp;height=324 1x\"></span><ul><li><p>On the Tools, Vector Displacement Map, set <em>vd Tangent</em> on, set <em>vd 32 Bit</em> to export a 32-bit map otherwise it is 16-bit, set <em>vd SUV</em> for smooth UV to on, <em>vd Normals</em> to on. </p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispMapExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562762&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=229\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/vectorDispMapExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562762&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"464\" data-width=\"709\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540832\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"vectorDispMapExport.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"fe56ea7b-894a-4f24-87d7-ec7c34cebb81\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispMapExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562762&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=700&amp;height=458 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispMapExport.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562762&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=229 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Click on CreateAndExport VDMap to export the maps and OBJ. The maps will be exported as OpenEXR.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ZBrushVectorDisplacement-ImportOBJandAddSubdivScheme\">Import OBJ and Add Subdiv Scheme</h3><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"e8740acf-7fee-4733-9c95-4c03f103b42f\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>For some subdivision surfaces, it may be helpful to add the attribute &quot;Dice Watertight&quot; to resolve seam issues. This may incur a memory overhead so it is not on by default.</p></div></div><p /><ul><li><p>Import the OBJ you just exported from ZBrush.  For its shape node, add <strong>Attributes|RenderMan|Subdiv Scheme:</strong></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"516\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=367&amp;height=119\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"119\" data-width=\"367\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540856\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"subdivScheme.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"46f28ca4-08d1-42fb-b810-c16699d36dbb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=367&amp;height=119 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/subdivScheme.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=367&amp;height=119 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"ZBrushVectorDisplacement-AssignDisplacementShader\">Assign Displacement Shader</h3><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrTexture</strong> node. Set the Filename to your exported ZBrush EXR map. Keep all parameters at their defaults.</p></li><li><p>Create a<strong> PxrDispTransform</strong> node. Set Displacement Type to <strong>ZBrush Vector</strong> and Vector Space to <strong>Tangent</strong>.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"574\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=433&amp;height=266\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"266\" data-width=\"433\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540838\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDispTransform.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"c2902d88-361f-488d-8e9f-95d552f88efe\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=433&amp;height=266 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/PxrDispTransform.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=433&amp;height=266 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Create a <strong>PxrDisplace</strong> node (this is the displacement shader that actually displaces your surface).</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrTexture's output Result RGB to PxrDispTransform's Disp Vector.</p></li><li><p>Connect PxrDispTransform's Result XYZ to PxrDisplace's Disp Vector. Your graph should look like this:</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=366\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"394\" data-width=\"968\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540841\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"vectorDispGraph.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"30850a1d-144b-46d0-9b1e-341d080e40b8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=968&amp;height=394 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/vectorDispGraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562988&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=366 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>Add <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFM24&amp;title=PxrSurface\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrSurface</a>, assign it to the model and add some <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544541369/Lighting+in+Maya\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541369\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">lights</a>, set the displacement bound appropriately, and render!</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_vectorDispRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=575\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/zbrush_vectorDispRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"693\" data-width=\"723\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540853\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"zbrush_vectorDispRender.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"44d62439-0076-4181-8fe5-fc96e79aa637\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_vectorDispRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=723&amp;height=693 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/zbrush_vectorDispRender.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431563341&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=575 1x\"></span><p /><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540797/VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540823\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic_RenderMan.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540797\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"198f2701-ce71-4c44-ae6f-6f9ea0fed28c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1012 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540797/VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic_RenderMan.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431562391&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=506 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"e95598de-151f-4c35-9df2-7cd7b24c8293\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"ZBrushVectorDisplacement-MayaProject\">Maya Project</h3><p>Download a Maya Project and test the official Zbrush vector displacement scene.</p><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/21037457/zbrush_Vector_Displacement.zip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1709251084079&amp;api=v2&amp;download=true\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download RfM</a> </p><p>Or a rib file...</p><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/21037457/VD_Zbrush_Diagnostic.rib.zip?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1709251088871&amp;api=v2&amp;download=true\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download RIB</a></p></div></div><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
